    • deleteSession

      @Path("sessions/{session}") @DELETE void deleteSession(@PathParam("session") String sessionId, @DefaultValue("false") @QueryParam("isOffline") boolean offline)
      Delete given user session
      Parameters:
      sessionId - session ID
      offline - Parameter available since Keycloak server 24.0.2. Will be ignored on older Keycloak versions with the default value false.
      Throws:
      jakarta.ws.rs.NotFoundException - if the user session is not found
